author: CoolVision
description:
What’s it actually like to experience London in 2025? In this cinematic travel vlog, I explore the city beyond the tourist brochures — from royal landmarks and buzzing markets to quiet neighborhoods and everyday moments that most visitors never see.

This isn’t your typical travel guide — it’s my honest journey through the world’s most iconic city. Expect history, contrast, beauty, and the real pulse of London life.

📍 Places Featured: Buckingham Palace, Westminster, Tower Bridge, Camden Market, Borough Market, Primrose Hill, Fleet Street, Kenwood House, and more.
title: London — Europe’s Most Visited City: What It’s Really Like in 2025?
